Mojolicious::Plugin::SassRenderer
=================================

A plugin for Mojolicious that allows you to include
Sass files in your templates and render them as CSS.

It uses Text::Sass to do this.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc Mojolicious::Plugin::SassRenderer

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=Mojolicious-Plugin-SassRenderer

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/Mojolicious-Plugin-SassRenderer

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/Mojolicious-Plugin-SassRenderer

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Mojolicious-Plugin-SassRenderer/


